### Add OTEL Logs API Support in Node.js

Source: https://github.com/newrelic/node-newrelic/blob/main/NEWS.md

Introduces support for the OpenTelemetry (OTEL) Logs API within the New Relic Node.js agent. This allows for capturing and sending logs that conform to the OTEL standard to New Relic.

```javascript
// Integration with OTEL logs API.
