### Node.js Agent Shutdown Method

Source: https://github.com/newrelic/node-newrelic/blob/main/NEWS.md

This snippet demonstrates how the `shutdown` method is now available on the stub API when the New Relic Node.js agent is disabled. Previously, this method was missing from the stub API.

```javascript
const newrelic = require('newrelic');

// ... agent is disabled ...

// The stub API now has the shutdown method
newrelic.shutdown();
```

