### Record Errors with .noticeError API - Node.js

Source: https://github.com/newrelic/node-newrelic/blob/main/NEWS.md

Introduces the `.noticeError` API call, allowing developers to report errors from anywhere in their application, not just within web requests. This provides a more comprehensive error tracking mechanism. No specific dependencies are mentioned for this functionality.

```javascript
newrelic.noticeError(error);
```

