### Obfuscate SQL using New Relic API in Node.js

Source: https://github.com/newrelic/node-newrelic/blob/main/NEWS.md

Exposes a method `newrelic.obfuscateSql` to obfuscate SQL queries. This is useful for security and reducing noise in database monitoring. The function takes a SQL string as input and returns the obfuscated string.

```javascript
const obfuscatedSql = newrelic.obfuscateSql(sqlString);
```
